                "name": "Player Core",
                "page": 233,
                "type": "source"
              }
            ],
            "text": "When you fall more than 5 feet, you take falling damage when you land, which is bludgeoning damage equal to half the distance you fell. If you take any damage from a fall, you're knocked prone when you land. You can Grab an Edge as a reaction to reduce or eliminate the damage from some falls. More detailed rules for falling damage appear here.",
            "type": "section"
          }
        ],
